DIARRHEAL DISEASES, BIBLIOGRAPHY
================================
Date: Fri, 28 Mar 1997 09:47:53 +0500
From: "Dan Campbell" <CAMPBELLDB@cdm.com>
Subject: Information on prevention of diarrheal diseases

The library of the USAID sponsored Environmental Health Project (EHP) has
recently published an annotated bibliography on the prevention of diarrheal
diseases. The bibliography contains 73 detailed abstracts of reports
published from 1992 through 1996 on steps taken to prevent cholera outbreaks
and other diarrheal diseases.

Send an email with your postal mailing address if you would like a copy, and
the bibliography is also available via our web site at:

http://www.access.digex.net/~ehp

(In the "What's New" section)

---
Dan Campbell, EHP Librarian
